===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HPE has provided the following software update to resolve the vulnerabilities
in HPE Helion OpenStack.

Helion OpenStack v1.1.3 customers should engage with HPE Helion Professional
Services through existing support channels to assist with the upgrade to
v1.1.4.

Helion OpenStack v2.1.4 can be downloaded from https://helion.hpwsportal.com/
catalog.html#/Product/%7B%22productId%22%3A%223034%22%7D/Show

Note: Follow the documentation at
http://docs.hpcloud.com/#helion/installation/upgrade_to_214.html

